    <text type="letter">
        <body>
            <pb xml:id="leaf001r" facs="loc.02571.001_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <opener>
                <dateline>
                    <name type="place"><handShift rend="printed"/>J. H. JOHNSTON, <lb/>DIAMOND
                        MERCHANT, <lb/>150 BOWERY, COR. BROOME ST.</name>
                    <date when="1887-09-10"><handShift rend="printed"/>New York, <handShift
                            rend="manuscript"/>Sept 10 <handShift rend="printed"/>188<handShift
                            rend="manuscript"/>7</date></dateline>
                <salute>Dear Walt;</salute>
            </opener>
            <p>The inclosed explains itself,<ptr target="loc.03613_n1"/> Either a forgery as well as
                theft has been committed or else you have had happen to you what has happened to me
                and I'm only 50 <choice>
                    <abbr>yrs</abbr>
                    <expan>years</expan>
                </choice> old&#8212; </p>
            <p>Viz: I have <choice>
                    <abbr>rec'd</abbr>
                    <expan>received</expan>
                </choice> a draft, endorsed it, deposited it, and forgot to give my customer credit
                for it. It happens, and will happen a thousand times. </p>
            <p>An interruption, a call of a friend, or a dozen other things will make me do what
                they will never believe they have done until forced to. Maybe this Postal Card will
                    <pb xml:id="leaf001v" facs="loc.02571.002_large.jpg" type="verso"/> be a
                reminder to you.</p>
            <p>I am coming over to your celebration next week and will help you straighten out the
                matter.</p>
            <p>I have written to Mr Shields and asked him to send me the draft.</p>
            <p>Alma<ptr target="n3029"/> and the boys return today.</p>
            <closer>
                <salute>With Love</salute>
                <salute>Sincerely yrs</salute>
                <signed><hi rend="underline">JH Johnston</hi></signed>
            </closer>

            <pb xml:id="leaf002r" facs="loc.02571.003_large.jpg" type="recto"/>
            <pb xml:id="leaf002v" facs="loc.02571.004_large.jpg" type="verso"/>
